            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName key="#Nuns/sanctimoniales"><name ref="Cleomnia "
                                >Cleomnia</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Nuns/sanctimoniales">religiosa femina</rs>, eo quod ante hos dies
                        bone memorie <persName><name ref="Ostribertus">Ostripert</name></persName>
                        domnus meus tertia portione ex omnibus rebus suis <rs
                            key="#Offersio/donatio">per cartula in eclesia firmavet</rs> et donavet;
                        et sic decrevit animus suus ut, ubi mihi placueret, in ipso loco <rs
                            key="#Churches">eclesia</rs>
                        <rs key="#Private_foundations">a fundamentis construere devirem</rs> in
                        honore <orgName key="#Churches #Private_foundations"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/255">beati sancti Cassiani</orgName>, sicut et
                        post decesso eius modo presenti a me factum est ita. Unde in mea reservavet
                        potestate, omnia et in omnibus usufructu de ipsa tertia portione quod in
                        ipsa eclesia offerserat, ut die vite me ipsa tertia portionem ego
                        usufructuarem. Modo in Dei nomine a fundamentis construxi ipsa Dei eclesia,
                        volo et offero Deo et tibi <rs key="#Churches">eclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/255">beati
                            Cassiani</orgName> medietate ex omnibus usufructu de ipsa tertia
                        portione quod in mea potestate dedet supradictus domnus meus Ostripert, ut
                        sacerdus in predicta eclesia ordinatus fuerit (…). Similiter offero in
                        predicta eclesia tertia portione ex <rs key="#Landed_possessions">omnibus
                            rebus</rs> meis quod <rs key="#Morgengabe">morghincap</rs> mihi datum
                        est, <foreign>affinché il prete preghi per lei e faccia la luminaria.
                            Scrive</foreign>: <persName key="#Writer #Subdeacons"><name
                                ref="Osprandus">Osprandum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Subdeacons">subdiaconum</rs>. (…) Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/716">Vico</placeName>. <foreign>Sottoscrizioni:</foreign> +
                        Cleomnie religiose femine; + <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Ostrifunsus">Ostrifusi</name></persName> filio eius; +
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Richibrandus"
                            >Richiprand</name></persName> germano ipsei femine testis; + <persName
                            key="#Witness #Vir_devotus/vir_honestus"><name ref="Aufusus"
                                >Aufusi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">viri devoti</rs> filio quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Auricundulus">Auriqualdali</name></persName>
                        testis; + <persName key="#Witness #Other_clerics #Vir_devotus/vir_honestus"
                                ><name ref="Ildebrandus">Ilprand</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clerici</rs>
                        <rs key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">viri devoti</rs> filio quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Albertus">Alpert</name></persName> testis;
                            <foreign>copia:</foreign>
                        <persName key="#Copyist"><name ref="Osprandus">Osprand</name></persName>
                        scriptor.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
